- [ ] Verify data accuracy against WhatsApp source
- [ ] Confirm template compliance (Report Templates folder)
- [ ] Check JSON schema consistency
- [ ] Validate equipment codes and BEV analysis
- [ ] Approve or request corrections

### Review Priority
